1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"腳踭?<br />\n<br />\n樣樣都試下啦,, 拉筋, 踩網球, 游水, 加扁平足鞋墊, 買鞋要有軟底, 同足弓位有弧度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:12:07.000Z","msg":"唔該哂大家先，但想問下佢本身唔係扁平足，買扁平足鞋墊有冇問題？<br />\n同埋佢本身都有幾嚴重既香港腳，會唔會有啲係唔做得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"我去買鞋墊講筋膜炎，佢就比扁平足墊我<br />\n<br />\n雖然係兩種問題，但舒緩方法差唔多，都係頂高足弓令壓力唔好長期集中係腳踭<br />\n<br />\n老實講未必醫得好，後生都仲好d，老左既話多數係仲筋退化，退化當然無得回復<br />\n<br />\n我之前都有香港腳，好返幾個月，同筋膜無乜關係，簡單睇就係長期唔識護理雙腳"},{"pid":"b1c285d70f12f40fcc26187499e172b4be53c962","tid":845964,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92e991a986a240d0ed20de7fef9769c5564a6e92","tid":845964,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"458d652f4c66eff6c83aeae0793a1d978261467a","tid":845964,"uid":104258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eef87463b487664cc5a8153598793945f4adb801","tid":845964,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"我爸爸都有<br />\n最後用部機舒緩返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"咩機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:11:20.000Z","msg":"一部去痛症既機<br />\n手掌咁大到<br />\n好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"有無樣睇？？ 叫咩名"},{"pid":"a998f533f61f8604ae1fd012934d02adf8801c78","tid":845964,"uid":104258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1c285d70f12f40fcc26187499e172b4be53c962","tid":845964,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92e991a986a240d0ed20de7fef9769c5564a6e92","tid":845964,"uid":85030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"458d652f4c66eff6c83aeae0793a1d978261467a","tid":845964,"uid":104258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T05:52:22.0